mixin Form()
    
    section.contacts
        .container.contacts__container
            form.form.reveal-left(action="thanks_form.php" method="POST" id='contact_form' class="contact_form")
                .contacts__text
                    h1.title Get in Touch with Us!
                    p.subtitle Have any questions or need assistance? We're here to help! Get in touch with us:

                .form__inputs

                    input.form__input(type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" required="")

                    input.form__input(type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required="")


                    label.form__checkbox
                        input(type="checkbox" name="privacy" value="on" required="")
                        span I agree to the processing of data
                    button.form__btn.btn(type="submit") Send Message
    section.contacts__container.contacts__container_bg
        .container.reveal-zoom
            h2  Have any questions or need assistance?
            p We're here to help! Whether you're looking for support, want to share feedback, or just need more information about our fantasy cricket platform, feel free to reach out. We are committed to providing you with prompt and helpful responses.
            p Our team is ready to assist you with any issues or inquiries you may have. Simply fill out the contact form above or use the contact details provided, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible. Your experience with VirtualCricketLeague is important to us!
            p If you have any questions, concerns, or suggestions, don't hesitate to get in touch with us. We're always ready to listen and assist you in any way we can.

            p Our goal is to ensure that your experience with VirtualCricketLeague is smooth and enjoyable. Whether you need technical support, have queries about the platform, or simply want to share your feedback, we are here for you.

            h3 You can contact us via the following methods:

            p Email: Reach out to us at 
                a(href='mailto:contact@virtualcricketleague.com') contact@virtualcricketleague.com 
                | for any inquiries or issues.
            p Phone: Call us at 
                a(href='tel:+919876234051') 
                | +91 987 623 4051 for immediate assistance.
            p We value your input and strive to continuously improve our service to meet your needs.
    
    
    
